WEBVTT

00:02:59.171 --> 00:03:01.198
don't go to school.

00:03:01.198 --> 00:03:03.623
They pretty much do nothing.

00:03:03.623 --> 00:03:07.139
I went back to Mogadishu last month,

00:03:07.139 --> 00:03:09.149
and I went to visit Madina Hospital,

00:03:09.149 --> 00:03:11.197
the hospital I was born in.

00:03:11.197 --> 00:03:13.222
I remember standing in front of that

00:03:13.222 --> 00:03:16.200
bullet-ridden hospital thinking,

00:03:16.200 --> 00:03:18.233
what if I had never left?

00:03:18.233 --> 00:03:19.426
What if I had been forced

00:03:19.426 --> 00:03:21.945
into that same state of waithood?

00:03:21.945 --> 00:03:25.956
Would I have become a terrorist?

00:03:25.956 --> 00:03:28.847
I'm not really sure about the answer.

00:03:28.847 --> 00:03:31.015
My reason for being in Mogadishu that month